You can extract the Jira SSL certificate directly as a .crt file from your Jenkins server (or any Linux box) in one clean command. Below are 3 reliable methods â€” use Method 1 (recommended).

â¸»

âœ… Method 1: Directly download Jira cert as .crt (BEST)

