Then split them:

awk '/BEGIN CERTIFICATE/{i++}{print > "jira-chain-" i ".crt"}' <(openssl s_client -connect jira.company.com:443 -showcerts </dev/null)

Import root + intermediate, not the leaf cert.

â¸»

ğŸ” Import into Jenkins Java truststore

